        <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-size:0.9rem; margin-top:0.375rem;">Training examples can be enough for a strong fine-tuned model</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p style="color:#00e3fd; font-size:2.25rem; font-weight:800; line-height:1;">40–60%</p>
