      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">gavel</span></div>
        <h3>Industry-Specific Knowledge</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7;">Legal, medical, financial, or technical domains where general models hallucinate or use imprecise terminology. Fine-tuning on domain data gives you expert-level precision.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
